            "description": "Upload required documents (Emirates ID, Passport, etc.)\n\n‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT: You need to upload actual files here!\n- Min: 1 file\n- Max: 5 files\n- Types: JPEG, PNG, WebP, PDF\n- Max size per file: 10MB"
          },
